{"tid":1037164,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我啱啱發左個夢！！！！","createTime":"2019-02-25T17:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T18:51:37.000Z","uid":135400,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"046841ec1e015644a0301709df76e21152f5d3ac","tid":1037164,"uid":135400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T17:33:50.000Z","msg":"發夢去跑渣馬障礙物10k馬拉松！！！<br />\n之後大家一齊起跑，一班人向前衝，但大部份人都情侶，一大班朋友咁跑，得我一個毒撚跑。<br />\n咁呢我就慢慢行，等班人走左。我就開始跑啦。<br />\n跑呀跑！！！<br />\n我好快咁就衝到返終點啦！<br />\n終點無乜人。<br />\n<br />\n然後！！！有人拎住個牌比我上面寫住我今次成績：33分xx秒！！！第二名！<br />\n<br />\n然後隔離工作人員拎d好似結婚d禮炮出黎咁，向我射彩帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我好開心好興奮<br />\n<br />\n之後佢即時帶我去頒獎：有個銀色盤有塊布係上面。咁d工作人員叫我拉開上面塊布<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我一拉<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仆街！！！！媽咪麵？？！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我呆左呆&hellip;之後有兩個工作人員一左一右咁挾住我<br />\n<br />\n之後挾住我&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;去返跑道&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有個牌&hellip;&hellip;有個牌寫住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二名嘅獎品係：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">媽咪麵免費請你！可以即時再挑戰一次</span></span>仲唔快，d返去挑戰第一！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後佢地挾我係起點度，一齊推左我背向前：大嗌！！！跑啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n我就笑到醒左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b4c16c33a59fdd2533ed5bcbdc3aaa50338a16","tid":1037164,"uid":137453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T17:36:39.000Z","m